    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2007-04-23</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2007-06-01T20:57:26Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Supports the goals and ideals of the Day of Silence (during which students vow to remain silent to bring attention to the harassment and discrimination faced by lesbian, gay, bisexual, and transgender people in schools). Encourages each city and state to adopt laws to prohibit discrimination and harassment against students, teachers, and other school staff regardless of their sexual orientation and gender identity and expression. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Supporting the goals and ideals of the Day of Silence with respect to discrimination and harassment faced by lesbian, gay, bisexual, and transgender individuals in schools.</title>
